    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "im just trying to get through my shift at work and i cant focus like this. it doesnt feel like an emergency or anything, it's just a dull ache. i've taken it before when my kidneys were better and it was totally fine. how bad is the risk really for just one or two pills?",
